Name:		madgraph-auto
Version:	0.3.3.2
Synopsis:	automated program library for madgraph run
Description: 	automated program library for madgraph run  
License: 	GPL-3
License-file:	LICENSE
Author:		Ian-Woo Kim
Maintainer: 	Ian-Woo Kim <ianwookim@gmail.com>
